reviews.review_text: The store is very well maintained, very clean and tidy. And all the staffs greet the customers with smile and accommodate the orders very quick and thank each customers claiming their orders. The manager, which I forgot to check, she is so far the best Mcdonalds employee I have ever met. Very positive attitude and she makes sure nobody waits a long time for their food. Fries are fresh too!
Always quick, efficient and has a drive-thru. I have never waited more than 5 minutes in the drive-thru.
I have 2 kids, one is employee and the  other one is customer. They both love being there. Kid-friendliness: Play zone, happy meal and most loveable Fries

Food is always prepared hot and fresh. Coffee has never tasted old or as though it has been sitting too long. Time between ordering and completion of preparation is reasonable. Parking lot is generally never overfilled. Location can be challenging to enter/exit from main road during heavy traffic hours, read entry/exit onto 55ave is favourable.
Good service and usually quiet! They are finishing renovations! And blue pine did the landscaping and it looks FANTASTIC!
Amazing customer service by brown girl with glasses
I usually visit this store every morning and the quality of food that I receive is beyond delicious. The manager and the staff can be seen hardworking & smiling.

I like to go through the drive-thru and eat in my car (Im disabled) so if youre like me, heads up that you cant get from the drive-thru lane back into the parking lot. Youll have two left turns across the often busy #10 Highway. Other than that highly specific to me, it was a good stop. The good was fresh and hot, the staff quick and understood my quirky needs and were friendly.
Best and freshest McDonalds Ive been to! Clean and great service and food was fresh and hot!
Hey,, I went with my friend (Gurkirat)who is working here.  We ordered some burgers. Its very delicious and staff gave quick service. Thank you to all staff.

You gotta love McDonalds. Get great value for your money and you get a great meal. You can be healthy or we could go to the greasy side. But there something for everyone for the health nut to the one that wants just a fast treat. Get Something for the kids, a kids meal and the toy and memories to share. Theres always a treat for everyone and something that everyone like. You gotta love McDonalds

I ordered a French Vanilla Latte from an Abbotsford location, repeated my order twice, and they still managed to get it wrong. I stopped at the locations Drive-Thru and told them what happened. They manager and employee on shift gave me the coffee I wanted for free!!! So shout out to this store and those 2 Employees with a great attitude and excellent customer service so early in the morning! Thanks again Josie and Geo! You made that day so much better!

What I like about this place is the location. So convenient in and out of Langley. For the first time I tried a breakfast with the griddle. I didnt know but the griddle is a bit sweet which makes the whole combination very tasty. The only thing I dont like about this place is the mens bathroom because theres very little air circulation and theres a permanent fruit fly population throughout the year.
I love the staff... No other McDonalds has faster service with nicer staff. And 2 thumbs up to the manager that works weekdays... He deserves a raise.

This was my first out of the country McDonalds experience. It was clean and they had a whole climbing wall!!! The kids loved it. I didnt taste the difference of the 100% Canadian beef but it was still a satisfactory big mac. Thanks for being a road trip staple and introducing me to poutine fries.

THE BEST EVER GREAT customer service I have ever had in my whole entire experience eating in at any Mcdonalds. Fast service, always greet you with smile. Deliever your food with a smile and some nice courtesy. And I just love how they maintain cleanliness at the play place as I often take my kids here to play and eat their fav happy meal. Great job guys!!! I hope you can keep it up!!!

Probably one of the best locations in Burnaby new West. They definately encompass the quality service and cleanliness that McDonalds swears by. Ive worked for McDs before so I know what to expect and this location holds a high standard for sure! Ill always come back here!

Great service today. Have had some bad experiences but today Nick at the drive thru window was awesome. Was having a problem with the app and he promptly fixed the problem. Very satisfied with the service. The food was excellent as well. Will be back again.

This one is the cleanest Mac Donalds I have ever been to, the staff are very friendly, the food is always fresh and very quick service. I like that the owner is into Mac Donalds memorability, it look great when you come in the door and see the display case filled with it all

I dont give McDonalds 5 stars ever by normal standards. Today the McDonalds in Cloverdale, because of one young lady who went above and beyond and held no judgement was the deciding factor. I wish I had gotten your name doll. You deserve much recognition. It is March 28/21 at 7 ish am. I wish I knew your name doll. It should be yelled from the mountain tops and Mcdonalds should have you on posters depicting you as what they would want the perfect employee to exemplify. I am humbled by your selflessness and compassion to your fellow human. Bravo you are a *****(5 star)

I just went through the drive thru. I ordered my food, paid for it,  and got it. Its whats supposed happen :) ...... tbe 5 stars is because these guys always get my ordered right, unlike other drive thrus
We use there meet room for monthly meetings and always grab a drink (others dinner) while we are there.  Lots of parking at this location and order accuracy is pretty good!
Very good
Fresh and hot. Good for McDonalds quick bite definitely gives you your quick fix and keeps you full.
was fast through the drive-through, friendly, everything was correct
We have and always will love McDonalds.  On this visit we were cold and tired and needed to ear.  McDonalds is the best comfort food.
the decor at this location is unlike any other. Love the toy display! Service was fast, staff was friendly and food was hot!
I have never been to a McDonald where a staff asks me if my food is ok until that visit. It was not that busy, but still quite a few customers there, good staff.
One of the friendliest McD out there. The drive thru is very fast. Never an issue at this location.
Loving the deals and as always great service, have a soft spot for mc ds
Was the way Mcdonalds was supposed to be hot, tasty and made me feel dirty afterwards.

This location is going through some renovations at the moment.. cant wait to see the improvements
quick service with large parking lot. Turning out of property is sometimes very busy on the road.

A very clean premise compared to other competitors. Food was hot and tasty served by professional and friendly staff.
The lady in front was really nice. Best customer service.
100 time better than the Mcdonalds on 64th and 176th, friendly and quick.
Kids absolutely love this spot for some play time and some delicious happy meals. Thanks McDonalds
It was wonderful, they gave us courtesy coffee and orange juice
My favorite McDonalds due to the Western theme. Excellent price of $1.05 for a large coffee.
I am very thankful to have McD nearby my location. Only restaurant to have open 24 hours
I like the renovation and the memorabilia. Clean and nice service.
8:30 am almost empty enjoyed a coffee in peace and quiet
Clean friendly staff and the coffee was hot
Tough to rate a McDonalds. It is what it is ..... fast and clean location.
